pageContext.claim: “So you have spent three straight years attempting to overturn the will of the American people and nullify their votes. You view democracy as your enemy!”
pageContext.analysis: Democrats have run investigations into the president for nearly three years. The first were prompted after Russia interfered in the 2016 election with the intention of supporting Trump’s White House bid. Investigations are not the same as an “attempt to overturn the will of the American people.”
